Ishuri Rikuru ry’Ubukorikori n’Ubumenyi rusange bw’imibereho (CASS) ni rimwe muri kaminuza esheshatu (6) zo muri kaminuza yu Rwanda (UR).<ref>https://schoolsinrwanda.com/listing/college-of-arts-and-social-sciences-cass-university-of-rwanda-ur/</ref> Iyi kaminuza ikaba yarashinzwe mu 2013 nkuko bigaragazwa mu itegeko no38 ryo ku wa 23/09/2013).<ref>https://applyintake.net/ur-college-of-arts-and-social-sciences-cass-history/</ref> Icyicaro gikuru cya CASS giherereye mumajyepfo y'u Rwanda mu kigo cya Huye ariko gikorera mu bigo bitandatu (Huye, Gikondo, Remera, Gako, Musanze na Nyakinama), kandi gifite abakozi bo mu kigo gishinzwe guteza imbere ururimi ku bigo byose bya kaminuza y'u Rwanda.

CASS igizwe n'amashuri ane (Ishuri ry'ubuhanzi n'indimi, ishuri ry'itangazamakuru n'itumanaho, ishuri ry'imiyoborere n'ishuri ry'amategeko), ibigo bine (Ikigo gishinzwe guteza imbere ururimi (CLE), Ikigo cy’ubushakashatsi ku buringanire (CGS), Ikigo cyo Gukemura amakimbirane (CCM), hamwe n’ikigo gishinzwe ubufasha mu by'amategeko (CLAM) na Radio yitwa Radio Salus.
